properties.areaDesc: Rock Island Passage to Sturgeon Bay WI; Green Bay south of line from  Cedar River to Rock Island Passage and north of a line from Oconto WI to Little Sturgeon Bay WI
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 4 at 3:18PM CST until January 6 at 9:00AM CST by NWS Green Bay WI
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southwest to west winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to
around 30 kt expected.

* WHERE...Green Bay south of line from Cedar River to Rock Island
Passage and north of a line from Oconto WI to Little Sturgeon
Bay WI and Lake Michigan from Rock Island Passage to Sturgeon
Bay WI.

* WHEN...From 10 AM Sunday to 9 AM CST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 10 AM SUNDAY TO 9 AM CST MONDAY
